
Variables
           --------------
->>Containers for storing data values.
->>It is created immediately you assign a value to it. ie
            name = "John"
            unit = "python language"
            college = "Catholic"
            print('my name is' + John + 'a student at' + college + 'and am currently learning ' + unit)
->>They can change type after some times. ie
            name = "James" # when you print name, it will output james not john.       
